snippet.title: Rayman Legends - Gloo Gloo Trailer [US]
snippet.description: Watch this all-new musical map just announced for Rayman Legends! Jump, punch, kick and swim your way to this classic song! Pick up Rayman Legends on September 3rd to experience all 120+ levels for yourself!
